<div id=3D"S2.SS1.p1" class=3D"ltx_para">
<p id=3D"S2.SS1.p1.1" class=3D"ltx_p">Transformer-based <cite class=3D"ltx_=
cite ltx_citemacro_cite">Vaswani<span class=3D"ltx_text ltx_bib_etal"> et a=
l.</span> [<a href=3D"https://arxiv.org/html/2511.05476#bib.bib1" title=3D"=
Attention is all you need" class=3D"ltx_ref">2017</a>]</cite> language mode=
ls of code have demonstrated remarkable performance across a wide range of =
software analytics tasks, such as vulnerability prediction, clone detection=
, code summarization, code completion, code comment generation, and code se=
arch <cite class=3D"ltx_cite ltx_citemacro_cite">Feng<span class=3D"ltx_tex=
t ltx_bib_etal"> et al.</span> [<a href=3D"https://arxiv.org/html/2511.0547=
6#bib.bib138" title=3D"Codebert: a pre-trained model for programming and na=
tural languages" class=3D"ltx_ref">2020</a>], Guo<span class=3D"ltx_text lt=
x_bib_etal"> et al.</span> [<a href=3D"https://arxiv.org/html/2511.05476#bi=
b.bib140" title=3D"Graphcodebert: pre-training code representations with da=
ta flow" class=3D"ltx_ref">2020</a>], Lu<span class=3D"ltx_text ltx_bib_eta=
l"> et al.</span> [<a href=3D"https://arxiv.org/html/2511.05476#bib.bib378"=
 title=3D"Codexglue: a machine learning benchmark dataset for code understa=
nding and generation" class=3D"ltx_ref">2021</a>], Ahmad<span class=3D"ltx_=
text ltx_bib_etal"> et al.</span> [<a href=3D"https://arxiv.org/html/2511.0=
5476#bib.bib162" title=3D"Unified pre-training for program understanding an=
d generation" class=3D"ltx_ref">2021</a>], Wang<span class=3D"ltx_text ltx_=
