bib141" title=3D"Codet5: identifier-aware unified pre-trained encoder-decod=
er models for code understanding and generation" class=3D"ltx_ref">2021b</a=
>], Devlin [<a href=3D"https://arxiv.org/html/2511.05476#bib.bib132" title=
=3D"Bert: pre-training of deep bidirectional transformers for language unde=
rstanding" class=3D"ltx_ref">2018</a>], Liu [<a href=3D"https://arxiv.org/h=
tml/2511.05476#bib.bib133" title=3D"Roberta: a robustly optimized bert pret=
raining approach" class=3D"ltx_ref">2019</a>], Sanh [<a href=3D"https://arx=
iv.org/html/2511.05476#bib.bib134" title=3D"DistilBERT, a distilled version=
 of bert: smaller, faster, cheaper and lighter" class=3D"ltx_ref">2019</a>]=
, Husain<span class=3D"ltx_text ltx_bib_etal"> et al.</span> [<a href=3D"ht=
tps://arxiv.org/html/2511.05476#bib.bib147" title=3D"Codesearchnet challeng=
