e models of code" class=3D"ltx_ref">2024a</a>, <a href=3D"https://arxiv.org=
/html/2511.05476#bib.bib10" title=3D"Efficient and green large language mod=
els for software engineering: vision and the road ahead" class=3D"ltx_ref">=
