</div>
<div id=3D"S3.SS1.SSS1.p2" class=3D"ltx_para">
<p id=3D"S3.SS1.SSS1.p2.1" class=3D"ltx_p"><span id=3D"S3.SS1.SSS1.p2.1.1" =
class=3D"ltx_text ltx_font_italic">Compressor</span>, <span id=3D"S3.SS1.SS=
S1.p2.1.2" class=3D"ltx_text ltx_font_italic">AVATAR</span>, and <span id=
=3D"S3.SS1.SSS1.p2.1.3" class=3D"ltx_text ltx_font_italic">MORPH</span> gen=
erate deployable models from language models of code using neural architect=
ure search guided by multi-objective optimization. <span id=3D"S3.SS1.SSS1.=
p2.1.4" class=3D"ltx_text ltx_font_italic">Compressor</span> explores vario=
us architecture-related hyperparameters, including the <span id=3D"S3.SS1.S=
