he feed-forward layers</span>, and <span id=3D"S3.SS1.SSS1.p2.1.9" class=3D=
"ltx_text ltx_font_italic">vocabulary size</span>. Whereas, both <span id=
=3D"S3.SS1.SSS1.p2.1.10" class=3D"ltx_text ltx_font_italic">AVATAR</span> a=
