on parameters include the choice of <span id=3D"S3.SS1.SSS1.p2.1.12" class=
=3D"ltx_text ltx_font_italic">tokenizer</span> (<span id=3D"S3.SS1.SSS1.p2.=
1.13" class=3D"ltx_text ltx_font_italic">BPE</span>, <span id=3D"S3.SS1.SSS=
1.p2.1.14" class=3D"ltx_text ltx_font_italic">WordPiece</span>, <span id=3D=
