class=3D"ltx_text ltx_font_italic">gelu</span>, <span id=3D"S3.SS1.SSS1.p2.=
1.22" class=3D"ltx_text ltx_font_italic">relu</span>, <span id=3D"S3.SS1.SS=
S1.p2.1.23" class=3D"ltx_text ltx_font_italic">silu</span>, and <span id=3D=
