m_{x\in X}\mathbf{1}\!\left[D_{\mathrm{KL}}\!\bigl(P_{T}(\cdot\mid x),P_{S}=
(\cdot\mid x)\bigr)\leq\delta\right]\qquad" display=3D"block" intent=3D":li=
teral"><semantics><mrow><msub><mtext>Loyalty</mtext><mtext>prob</mtext></ms=
