}" display=3D"inline" intent=3D":literal"><semantics><msub><mtext>Loyalty</=
mtext><mtext>prob</mtext></msub><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">=
\text{Loyalty}_{\text{prob}}</annotation></semantics></math> indicates that=
 the student model retains the teacher model=E2=80=99s probability-distribu=
tion behavior on a greater portion of the test set.</p>
