 must predict the same top-1 class as <math id=3D"S4.SS2.SSS3.Px1.p4.2.m2" =
class=3D"ltx_Math" alttext=3D"M_{T}" display=3D"inline" intent=3D":literal"=
><semantics><msub><mi>M</mi><mi>T</mi></msub><annotation encoding=3D"applic=
ation/x-tex">M_{T}</annotation></semantics></math> <em id=3D"S4.SS2.SSS3.Px=
1.p4.3.1" class=3D"ltx_emph ltx_font_italic">and</em> do so with confidence=
