<h5 class=3D"ltx_title ltx_font_bold ltx_title_paragraph">Evaluation metric=
</h5>

<div id=3D"S4.SS2.SSS4.Px3.p1" class=3D"ltx_para">
<p id=3D"S4.SS2.SSS4.Px3.p1.1" class=3D"ltx_p">We propose the <em id=3D"S4.=
SS2.SSS4.Px3.p1.1.1" class=3D"ltx_emph ltx_font_italic">Expected Calibratio=
n Alignment</em> (ECA) metric, defined as the mean absolute difference in b=
in-wise accuracy to assess this behavioral fidelity:</p>
</div>
