tx_Math" alttext=3D"\mathrm{ECA}\;=3D\;\frac{1}{B}\sum_{i=3D1}^{B}\left|\,\=
text{acc}^{\text{orig}}_{i}-\text{acc}^{\text{comp}}_{i}\right|" display=3D=
