isplay=3D"inline" intent=3D":literal"><semantics><msub><mtext>MR</mtext><mi=
>k</mi></msub><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">\text{MR}_{k}</ann=
otation></semantics></math> holds. Then, the violation rate is defined as:<=
/p>
</div>
<div id=3D"S4.SS2.SSS4.Px3.p5" class=3D"ltx_para">
