x">\max M_{T}(x)!\geq!\tau</annotation></semantics></math>); and (iv) maint=
ains aligned calibration curves such that the bin-wise accuracy difference =
<math id=3D"S4.SS2.SSS4.Px3.p7.2.m2" class=3D"ltx_Math" alttext=3D"\lvert\t=
ext{acc}^{\text{orig}}_{i}-\text{acc}^{\text{comp}}_{i}\rvert" display=3D"i=
