=E2=88=92</mo><msubsup><mtext>acc</mtext><mi>i</mi><mtext>comp</mtext></msu=
bsup></mrow><mo stretchy=3D"false">|</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=3D"app=
lication/x-tex">\lvert\text{acc}^{\text{orig}}_{i}-\text{acc}^{\text{comp}}=
_{i}\rvert</annotation></semantics></math> remains consistently small.</p>
</div>
