 class=3D"ltx_text ltx_ref_tag">7</span></a> presents the per-sample distri=
butions of these values for KD approaches: <span id=3D"S4.SS3.SSS2.p5.6.1" =
class=3D"ltx_text ltx_font_italic">Compressor</span>, <span id=3D"S4.SS3.SS=
S2.p5.6.2" class=3D"ltx_text ltx_font_italic" style=3D"font-size:120%;">A<s=
