ation alignment (<span id=3D"Sx1.1.p1.pic1.2.2.2.1.1.1.7" class=3D"ltx_text=
 ltx_font_bold">MR4</span>), <span id=3D"Sx1.1.p1.pic1.2.2.2.1.1.1.8" class=
